{
  "texts": [
    "The remainder of the paper is structured as follows.",
    "In section 2, we review related work on NLP-based patent analytics, p2p similarity measures, and automated patent classification.",
    "Section 3 introduces the patent dataset used as well as its properties and methodological choices with respect to the patent information used in our framework, namely patent claim text and patent CPC classification.",
    "Section 4 introduces our SBERT based hybrid framework for patent embedding, p2p similarity calculation, and automated patent classification.",
    "The following section 5 presents our results and provides a validation exercise for patent classification."
  ]
}